                    "type": "table",
                    "content": {
                        "title": "🔴 Common Confusions",
                        "headers": ["Word Pair", "Difference", "Example"],
                        "rows": [
                            ["<b>Older vs Elder</b>", "Older: वस्तु/व्यक्ति (उम्र में बड़ा)<br>Elder: केवल सगे भाई-बहन के लिए", "My friend is <b>older</b> than me.<br>She is my <b>elder</b> sister."],
                            ["<b>Farther vs Further</b>", "Farther: दूर (Distance)<br>Further: आगे (Next/More)", "Mumbai is <b>farther</b> than Surat.<br>Any <b>further</b> questions?"],
                            ["<b>Nearest vs Next</b>", "Nearest: सबसे पास (Distance)<br>Next: अगला (Sequence)", "Where is the <b>nearest</b> bank?<br>Who is <b>next</b>?"],
                            ["<b>Later vs Latter</b>", "Later: बाद में (Time)<br>Latter: दो में से दूसरा (Position)", "I will call you <b>later</b>.<br>The <b>latter</b> option is better."]
                        ]
                    }
                }
            ]
